#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="62"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.1.8.4" href="#Bu-Pj.1.8.4"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.102" href="#ms.102"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā?"
